Name: Quadratic puzzle 3
About the game: Game introduction The main goal of the game is to jigsaw puzzles, and it is necessary to splicing the disrupted pieces into suitable parts. When all is completed, it will be graded according to the time used. The grading scale is divided into 6 grades: 'SS', 'S', 'A', 'B', 'C', 'D'. Special cg content can also be unlocked whenever the score is 'S' or 'SS'. Game Features The pictures stitched together are very cute anime girls images. Rating 's' or 'ss' to unlock special CG, you know. Easy to operate, just click the mouse with your right hand to play the game. Support 7 languages and multiple resolutions.
